ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAnnex 7 of the International Health Regulations (2005) ** Amendment **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to accept, on behalf of the Government of Canada, that the AMENDMENT TO ANNEX 7 OF THE INTERNATIONAL HEALTH REGULATIONS (2005), adopted in Geneva on May 24, 2014, be binding on Canada.
